{"tid":771493,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大哨揀史上最佳陣容　C朗冇份","createTime":"2018-08-08T03:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T10:30:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":48,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"ae25777e6c2b53736b452f891bb34c55cabd2abf","tid":771493,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180807/photo/bkn-20180807193103638-0807_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180807202847\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180807%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180807193103638-0807_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180807202847&h=2258894e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西傳奇前鋒朗拿度日前接受《阿斯報》訪問，要佢揀出心目中史上最佳11人陣容，結果佢揀咗包括自己在內嘅4個巴西人，但就冇佢當年「3R」拍檔朗拿甸奴同李華度；另外仲有4個意大利人、2個阿根廷球員同1個法國球王施丹。數吓數吓都堅係齊腳，仲級數誇張，只係連一個德國球員都冇，新世代球王C朗拿度又冇，真係估佢唔到喎！<br />\n<br />\n大哨心目中最佳陣容：<br />\n門將：保方<br />\n後衞：卡富、簡拿華路、馬甸尼、卡路士<br />\n中場：馬納當拿、派路、施丹、美斯<br />\n前鋒：比利、朗拿度"},{"pid":"5632ea5f73421ba05994f2ec1e0a46e2fc27d42c","tid":771493,"uid":174530,"like":86,"dislike":48,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"牙朗勁過佢啦"},{"pid":"8a19a38454b87f0e4125e62fdf82c0aaac4a0235","tid":771493,"uid":4957,"like":22,"dislike":68,"score":-46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"On9 。。沙維》派路啦"},{"pid":"c752d2e83a8ce0d1f3ff1b2a521908437c62c05c","tid":771493,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"全攻型"},{"pid":"b88e1faf06c252cac87a6f87b881fd5e3a79b9e0","tid":771493,"uid":77327,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"用托度好過保方啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70ce1d4db1324c6f2a9f724d9022a410f8851da","tid":771493,"uid":134087,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"你叫佢揀一定揀啲同佢踢過啲人"},{"pid":"7c2f0ca8c4ba64a935510a2e1dd3164e17b6169b","tid":771493,"uid":5649,"l